 that fits both your style and your daily routine. In this kitchen rug buying guide, you'll learn how to pick the right material, size, and design to create a space that feels comfortable and looks just the way you want.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-cee1" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-dBFCZX khzvmY pf-25_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-gvPcJq dRaLso"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-26_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-27_"></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-28_"><img alt="c9fb06c8f3c2fe779368abdcba051f92.webp__PID:060da6fc-a928-4c65-9539-b538bcb2de57" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/c9fb06c8f3c2fe779368abdcba051f92.webp?v=1748264357&width=2048" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/c9fb06c8f3c2fe779368abdcba051f92.webp?v=1748264357&width=375 375w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/c9fb06c8f3c2fe779368abdcba051f92.webp?v=1748264357&width=550 550w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/c9fb06c8f3c2fe779368abdcba051f92.webp?v=1748264357&width=768 768w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/c9fb06c8f3c2fe779368abdcba051f92.webp?v=1748264357&width=1024 1024w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/c9fb06c8f3c2fe779368abdcba051f92.webp?v=1748264357&width=1280 1280w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/c9fb06c8f3c2fe779368abdcba051f92.webp?v=1748264357&width=1440 1440w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/c9fb06c8f3c2fe779368abdcba051f92.webp?v=1748264357&width=1680 1680w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/c9fb06c8f3c2fe779368abdcba051f92.webp?v=1748264357&width=1800 1800w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/c9fb06c8f3c2fe779368abdcba051f92.webp?v=1748264357&width=1920 1920w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/c9fb06c8f3c2fe779368abdcba051f92.webp?v=1748264357&width=2048 2048w" fetchPriority="low" decoding="async" loading="lazy" style="--pf-image-ratio:0.75" width="1170" height="1560" sizes="75vw" data-pf-type="Image4" class="sc-jlGhtx iHZcAb pf-29_" store="[object Object]"/></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-30_"></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-f22b" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-dBFCZX khzvmY pf-31_ pf-color-scheme-1"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-gvPcJq dRaLso"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-32_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-33_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cXPBhi kkWDYP pf-34_ pf-heading-1-h2"><i class="sc-dChVQp hgzReS pf-35_ pf-icon-1 pfa pfa-star pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide pf-hide" data-pf-type="Icon"></i>Benefits of Having a Kitchen Rug</h2></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-36_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-37_"><p class="sc-edLa-Dd hZPWCc pf-38_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">The kitchen is where your day starts, where meals are made, and where the mess often follows. A well-chosen rug makes the space easier to live in and more enjoyable to use. Here's how it helps:<br><br><strong>•  Keeps your floor cleaner and safer:</strong> Cooking gets messy. A rug catches splashes and crumbs before they reach the floor, helping to prevent stains, slips, and scratches.<br><br><strong>•  Makes long tasks more comfortable:</strong> When you're standing at the sink or stove for a while, a cushioned rug can ease pressure on your feet, legs, and back.<br><br><strong>•  Softens sound in a busy space:</strong> Kitchens are full of hard surfaces that echo. A rug helps absorb noise so the room feels calmer and less chaotic.<br><br><strong>•  Brings in your personal style:</strong> A rug is a simple way to show your taste. Whether you prefer bold patterns or soft neutrals, it makes the kitchen feel more like you.<br><br><strong>•  Helps guide how you use the space:</strong> In open layouts, rugs can separate the cooking area from the dining zone, making the room feel more organized and intentional.<br></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-40_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-41_"></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-42_"><img alt="8cd73379116e53a868f2bd4ebfa7d258.webp__PID:c3b6282d-4931-4673-b005-3623734a09c2" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/8cd73379116e53a868f2bd4ebfa7d258.webp?v=1754136333&width=2048" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/8cd73379116e53a868f2bd4ebfa7d258.webp?v=1754136333&width=375 375w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/8cd73379116e53a868f2bd4ebfa7d258.webp?v=1754136333&width=550 550w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/8cd73379116e53a868f2bd4ebfa7d258.webp?v=1754136333&width=768 768w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/8cd73379116e53a868f2bd4ebfa7d258.webp?v=1754136333&width=1024 1024w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/8cd73379116e53a868f2bd4ebfa7d258.webp?v=1754136333&width=1280 1280w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/8cd73379116e53a868f2bd4ebfa7d258.webp?v=1754136333&width=1440 1440w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/8cd73379116e53a868f2bd4ebfa7d258.webp?v=1754136333&width=1680 1680w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/8cd73379116e53a868f2bd4ebfa7d258.webp?v=1754136333&width=1800 1800w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/8cd73379116e53a868f2bd4ebfa7d258.webp?v=1754136333&width=1920 1920w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/8cd73379116e53a868f2bd4ebfa7d258.webp?v=1754136333&width=2048 2048w" fetchPriority="low" decoding="async" loading="lazy" style="--pf-image-ratio:0.6671608598962194" width="900" height="1349" sizes="75vw" data-pf-type="Image4" class="sc-jlGhtx iHZcAb pf-43_" store="[object Object]"/><h4 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cXPBhi kkWDYP pf-44_"><em><strong>Brings in your personal style<a href="https://www.lanyspace.com/collections/irregular-area-rugs" target="_self"></a></strong><a href="https://www.lanyspace.com/collections/irregular-area-rugs" target="_self"></a></em></h4></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-46_"></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-47_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-48_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cXPBhi kkWDYP pf-49_ pf-heading-1-h2"><i class="sc-dChVQp hgzReS pf-50_ pf-icon-1 pfa pfa-star pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide pf-hide" data-pf-type="Icon"></i>How to Choose the Right Material for a Kitchen Rug</h2></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-51_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-52_"><p class="sc-edLa-Dd hZPWCc pf-53_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Kitchens are full of heat, moisture, and spills, so not every rug is built to handle this kind of space. Choosing the right material makes a big difference in how long your rug lasts and how easy it is to keep clean.<br></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-55_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-56_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cXPBhi kkWDYP pf-57_">What to avoid</h3></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-59_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-60_"><p class="sc-edLa-Dd hZPWCc pf-61_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><strong>Jute or sisal:</strong> These natural fibers look nice, but they absorb water easily. That can lead to stains, odors, and a rug that loses shape over time.<br><br><strong>Cotton:</strong> Cotton rugs feel soft but tend to hold on to moisture. In a kitchen, they can take too long to dry and start to smell if spills aren't cleaned up quickly.<br><br><strong>Wool: </strong>Wool is thick and warm but not easy to maintain in a kitchen. It doesn't handle grease or frequent cleaning well and may not recover after heavy use.<br></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-63_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-64_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cXPBhi kkWDYP pf-65_">What works better</h3></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-67_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-68_"><p class="sc-edLa-Dd hZPWCc pf-69_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><a href="https://www.lanyspace.com/blogs/rug-inspirations-and-trends/why-lany-space-choose-polyester-to-make-rugs" target="_self"><u><span style="color: rgb(1, 126, 86);"></span></u><span style="color: rgb(1, 126, 86);"><u>Polyester</u></span></a> is one of the best materials for kitchen rugs. It's durable, easy to clean, and holds up well in busy areas. It resists water and stains, dries quickly, and feels soft underfoot. Many polyester rugs are also machine washable, which makes regular cleanup much simpler. If you want something that looks good and handles daily mess without extra fuss, this is the material to look for.<em><strong><br></strong></em></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-71_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-72_"><img title="polyester rug" alt="b6233380444637e3577aaeda2c126d3b_compressed.webp__PID:2c014e14-7187-4346-8832-bee863f866e2" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/b6233380444637e3577aaeda2c126d3b_compressed.webp?v=1754917330&width=2048" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/b6233380444637e3577aaeda2c126d3b_compressed.webp?v=1754917330&width=375 375w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/b6233380444637e3577aaeda2c126d3b_compressed.webp?v=1754917330&width=550 550w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/b6233380444637e3577aaeda2c126d3b_compressed.webp?v=1754917330&width=768 768w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/b6233380444637e3577aaeda2c126d3b_compressed.webp?v=1754917330&width=1024 1024w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/b6233380444637e3577aaeda2c126d3b_compressed.webp?v=1754917330&width=1280 1280w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/b6233380444637e3577aaeda2c126d3b_compressed.webp?v=1754917330&width=1440 1440w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/b6233380444637e3577aaeda2c126d3b_compressed.webp?v=1754917330&width=1680 1680w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/b6233380444637e3577aaeda2c12