uce chair noise. Make sure it's big enough so all chairs stay on the rug, even when pulled out.<br><br><strong>•  By the kitchen entrance:</strong> Place a rug near any back door or entry point to trap dirt and moisture. This helps keep the rest of the kitchen cleaner with less effort.<strong><em><br></em></strong></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-84_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:4;--c-sm:6;--c-md:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-85_"><img alt="250605@delaneyandblu 1.webp__PID:c9e234a0-b13f-401a-bc0f-ce4a5ff6df5b" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/250605_delaneyandblu_1.webp?v=1752295668&width=2048" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/250605_delaneyandblu_1.webp?v=1752295668&width=375 375w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/250605_delaneyandblu_1.webp?v=1752295668&width=550 550w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/250605_delaneyandblu_1.webp?v=1752295668&width=768 768w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/250605_delaneyandblu_1.webp?v=1752295668&width=1024 1024w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/250605_delaneyandblu_1.webp?v=1752295668&width=1280 1280w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/250605_delaneyandblu_1.webp?v=1752295668&width=1440 1440w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/250605_delaneyandblu_1.webp?v=1752295668&width=1680 1680w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/250605_delaneyandblu_1.webp?v=1752295668&width=1800 1800w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/250605_delaneyandblu_1.webp?v=1752295668&width=1920 1920w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/250605_delaneyandblu_1.webp?v=1752295668&width=2048 2048w" fetchPriority="low" decoding="async" loading="lazy" style="--pf-image-ratio:0.75" width="3024" height="4032" sizes="75vw" dat